data.description: Do you love hosting? This home is the one for you! This large two-story home features wood floors, new carpet, new paint inside and out, and a new water heater to name a few of the upgrades. The chef's kitchen includes a new double oven and granite countertops. The home has a wet bar that leads to an updated sunroom and an outside cabana that overlooks the beautiful inground pool. The cabana has its own private bathroom. The newly renovated sunroom features updated heating and air conditioning, new windows, and sliding glass doors with a perfect view of the pool and entertaining area. Schedule your appointment today!
